178
00:10:28,350 --> 00:10:30,470
Xia Shu, can you learn how to behave?

179
00:10:30,820 --> 00:10:32,020
What's wrong with me?

180
00:10:33,510 --> 00:10:35,480
I'm a formal lawyer now.

181
00:10:35,940 --> 00:10:37,500
Let's work together in the future.

182
00:10:37,500 --> 00:10:38,520
