205
00:11:24,940 --> 00:11:25,870
Absolutely not.

206
00:11:26,030 --> 00:11:27,330
I think you're amazing.

207
00:11:27,330 --> 00:11:28,450
I admire you.

208
00:11:28,840 --> 00:11:30,590
