222
00:12:01,000 --> 00:12:01,840
No, no.

223
00:12:01,840 --> 00:12:03,550
-Who complained? -No, no, no.

224
00:12:03,580 --> 00:12:04,220
Which one?

225
00:12:04,240 --> 00:12:04,680
No.

226
00:12:04,710 --> 00:12:05,310
Is it you?

227
00:12:05,330 --> 00:12:06,070
-No. -Do you have a complaint?

228
00:12:06,070 --> 00:12:07,300
No.

229
00:12:07,320 --> 00:12:07,850
Is it you?

230
00:12:07,870 --> 00:12:08,470
No.

231
00:12:08,530 --> 00:12:10,280
