237
00:12:21,260 --> 00:12:21,920
Fine.

238
00:12:23,080 --> 00:12:25,000
Think about my proposal.

239
00:12:26,070 --> 00:12:28,150
I'll read the case analysis first.

240
00:12:34,340 --> 00:12:35,220
I'll go then.

241
00:12:37,690 --> 00:12:38,480
I'm leaving.

242
00:12:41,850 --> 00:12:44,290
Think about it.

243
00:12:44,320 --> 00:12:45,570
Think about it.

244
00:12:56,400 --> 00:12:58,660
