00:15:02,790 --> 00:15:04,910
Xia Shu was promoted to be a partner.

293
00:15:05,610 --> 00:15:06,330
What?

294
00:15:07,940 --> 00:15:09,950
The law firm is so shameless.

295
00:15:10,130 --> 00:15:11,250
Of course it is.

296
00:15:11,950 --> 00:15:14,770
