297
00:15:14,770 --> 00:15:15,630
Think about it.

298
00:15:16,500 --> 00:15:17,900
She's coming.

299
00:15:26,430 --> 00:15:27,770
Mr. Tian, are you busy?

300
00:15:29,370 --> 00:15:29,930
Miss Xia.

301
00:15:30,130 --> 00:15:31,880
I'm going to get some water.

302
00:15:31,910 --> 00:15:32,510
Thank you.

303
00:15:33,850 --> 00:15:36,260
Looks like I have to continue to congratulate you.

304
00:15:36,260 --> 00:15:37,020
For what?

305
00:15:37,930 --> 00:15:39,640
Didn't you become a partner?

306
00:15:40,520 --> 00:15:41,180
Boring.

307
00:15:43,190 --> 00:15:43,900
Luo Yingzi.

308
00:15:44,750 --> 00:15:46,230
I know you don't want to be my partner,

309
00:15:46,230 --> 00:15:48,230
