311
00:15:51,320 --> 00:15:52,710
You shall give it to the firm first.

312
00:15:52,710 --> 00:15:53,430
No.

313
00:15:53,790 --> 00:15:55,400
This is from my classmate.

314
00:15:55,670 --> 00:15:57,410
He studied abroad

315
00:15:57,430 --> 00:15:59,370
and couldn't find a decent job when he came back.

316
00:15:59,370 --> 00:16:01,030
So, he served as a case broker,

317
00:16:01,190 --> 00:16:02,780
who specially introduced cases

318
00:16:02,780 --> 00:16:04,420
and got the commission.

319
00:16:04,620 --> 00:16:07,310
I'm not interested in playing with him. Do you want it?

320
00:16:07,310 --> 00:16:07,710
Yes.

321
00:16:08,390 --> 00:16:09,070
What case?

322
00:16:09,170 --> 00:16:10,130
A divorce case.

323
00:16:11,370 --> 00:16:12,210
Divorce case?

324
00:16:12,610 --> 00:16:13,950
Yeah, it must be boring.

325
00:16:14,840 --> 00:16:15,470
Never mind.

326
00:16:15,470 --> 00:16:17,070
If you don't want it, I'll introduce it to the Civil Affairs Department.

327
00:16:17,070 --> 00:16:18,070
No, no, no.

328
00:16:18,190 --> 00:16:19,160
As I think,

329
00:16:19,180 --> 00:16:20,370
it's improper to look down upon tiny cases.

330
00:16:20,370 --> 00:16:22,000
I don't have the right to be picky right now.

331
00:16:22,000 --> 00:16:23,880
Tell me about the divorce case.

332
00:16:49,830 --> 00:16:50,830
Mr. Yang?

333
00:16:51,010 --> 00:16:53,560
Hello, I'm Luo Yingzi, a lawyer.

334
00:16:53,610 --> 00:16:55,750
Yes, I'm recommended by Miss Xia.

335
00:16:56,440 --> 00:16:56,960
OK.

336
00:16:57,140 --> 00:16:59,420
Yes, I'd like to learn about your case.

337
00:16:59,590 --> 00:17:01,390
Can you introduce it to me?

338
00:17:01,950 --> 00:17:02,470
Okay.

339
00:17:03,220 --> 00:17:04,069
Wei

340
00:17:05,140 --> 00:17:06,750
Tongren.

341
00:17:08,010 --> 00:17:10,160
Chairman.

342
00:17:10,410 --> 00:17:11,720
General Manager.

343
00:17:13,780 --> 00:17:14,339
No.

344
00:17:14,470 --> 00:17:16,339
I always smile.

345
00:17:16,839 --> 00:17:18,000
Okay, go on.

346
00:17:18,030 --> 00:17:18,859
Okay.

347
00:17:20,119 --> 00:17:21,240
Don't worry.

348
00:17:21,480 --> 00:17:22,180
We know the rules.

349
00:17:22,180 --> 00:17:22,790
If I

350
00:17:22,790 --> 00:17:23,890
take this case,

351
00:17:24,109 --> 00:17:26,230
we can discuss the commission.

352
00:17:26,349 --> 00:17:28,300
We still have Miss Xia.

353
00:17:28,329 --> 00:17:28,970
Okay.

354
00:17:29,130 --> 00:17:30,380
Thank you. Bye.

355
00:17:30,790 --> 00:17:32,010
Chairman.

356
00:17:32,510 --> 00:17:34,490
Then I must win you.

357
00:17:37,160 --> 00:17:41,970
Tongren Road and Bridge Company.

358
00:17:43,200 --> 00:17:45,420
[Brief Introduction of Tongren Road and Bridge Construction Co., Ltd.]

359
00:17:49,870 --> 00:17:54,750
The market value is 1.1 billion.

360
00:17:55,380 --> 00:17:57,890
Are you out of your mind?

361
00:17:58,190 --> 00:18:01,110
Wei Tongren.

362
00:18:03,840 --> 00:18:06,690
Bro, you are so rich.

363
00:18:06,420 --> 00:18:08,870
[Wei Tongren, Chairman of Tongren Road and Bridge Construction Co., Ltd.]

364
00:18:06,730 --> 00:18:10,670
What's the use of your divorce?

365
00:18:15,440 --> 00:18:16,560
Xia Shu. Xia Shu.

366
00:18:18,440 --> 00:18:19,770
The case you introduced

367
00:18:19,910 --> 00:18:22,570
involves a large amount of money. Let's take it together.

368
00:18:22,570 --> 00:18:23,900
I'll work with Qiu Hua,

369
00:18:24,030 --> 00:18:25,230
and you take most of the legal fee.

370
00:18:25,230 --> 00:18:27,090
I'm not interested. I won't do it.

371
00:18:27,120 --> 00:18:28,130
Is this okay?

372
00:18:28,380 --> 00:18:29,470
Hold on. I'm testing.

373
00:18:29,470 --> 00:18:30,530
What are you doing?

374
00:18:30,910 --> 00:18:32,200
The firm is so slacking off.

375
00:18:32,200 --> 00:18:33,860
I complained about the slow Internet speed

376
00:18:33,860 --> 00:18:35,200
and asked them to speed it up.

377
00:18:35,200 --> 00:18:35,940
They want to

378
00:18:35,960 --> 00:18:37,310
install one router for my office.

379
00:18:37,310 --> 00:18:38,370
What about others?

380
00:18:38,490 --> 00:18:39,380
Be content.

381
00:18:39,880 --> 00:18:41,110
Are you sure not to take it?

382
00:18:41,110 --> 00:18:41,860
Yes.

383
00:18:41,880 --> 00:18:44,210
I didn't study law to solve a divorce case.

384
00:18:45,430 --> 00:18:47,800
This is not an ordinary divorce case.

385
00:18:47,820 --> 00:18:48,860
I checked it.

386
00:18:49,020 --> 00:18:50,170
The client

387
00:18:50,190 --> 00:18:52,430
has a company worth billions.

388
00:18:52,520 --> 00:18:54,130
Ten billion is also money.

389
00:18:54,160 --> 00:18:55,020
I won't take it.

390
00:18:55,440 --> 00:18:56,630
Please check the Internet speed.

391
00:18:56,630 --> 00:18:57,560
Okay, let me see.

392
00:19:00,630 --> 00:19:02,090
Do you like playing games?

393
00:19:02,630 --> 00:19:05,670
Okay, I'll give you some sets of game skins later.

394
00:19:06,100 --> 00:19:06,450
Good.

395
00:19:06,470 --> 00:19:07,200
I'm leaving.

396
00:19:07,830 --> 00:19:09,490
Are you sure you won't take it?

397
00:19:10,930 --> 00:19:11,430
I'm leaving.

398
00:19:11,430 --> 00:19:11,850
Bye.

399
00:19:31,180 --> 00:19:31,980
What's wrong?

400
00:19:32,080 --> 00:19:34,280
I have something important to tell you.

401
00:19:35,220 --> 00:19:36,420
Close the door first.

402
00:19:42,550 --> 00:19:43,960
That's a big case.

403
00:19:45,640 --> 00:19:47,170
Congratulations, Yingzi.

404
00:19:47,480 --> 00:19:48,890
But it is too valuable,

405
00:19:48,920 --> 00:19:50,180
and I can't do it alone.

406
00:19:50,310 --> 00:19:50,990
Why?

407
00:19:51,120 --> 00:19:52,190
At our age,

408
00:19:52,240 --> 00:19:53,700
when we come out to deal with cases independently,

409
00:19:53,700 --> 00:19:55,230
the clients won't trust us.

410
00:19:55,710 --> 00:19:56,230
Qiu Hua.

411
00:19:56,670 --> 00:19:57,870
Let's work together.

412
00:19:58,870 --> 00:20:01,390
We can't add our age together.

413
00:20:01,430 --> 00:20:01,900
No.

414
00:20:02,470 --> 00:20:05,450
You have a trustworthy face.

415
00:20:05,470 --> 00:20:07,740
Unlike me, I have a short-tempered face.

416
00:20:07,830 --> 00:20:08,790
Nonsense.

417
00:20:09,610 --> 00:20:11,010
I know you want to help me.

418
00:20:11,150 --> 00:20:12,610
I'm not trying to help you.

419
00:20:12,690 --> 00:20:13,960
I'm begging you to help me.

420
00:20:13,960 --> 00:20:15,090
Just like last time.

421
00:20:17,470 --> 00:20:18,160
Fine.

422
00:20:18,820 --> 00:20:20,650
This time, you take the case.

423
00:20:21,990 --> 00:20:23,990
-And our agency fee will be… -50-50.

424
00:20:24,740 --> 00:20:25,510
30-70.

425
00:20:25,660 --> 00:20:27,190
You get 70, and I get 30. Huh?

426
00:20:28,290 --> 00:20:28,990
Just kidding.

427
00:20:28,990 --> 00:20:29,550
I know.

428
00:20:29,740 --> 00:20:30,420
40-60.

429
00:20:30,440 --> 00:20:31,770
Stop bargaining. Deal.

430
00:20:32,640 --> 00:20:34,200
Ok, thank you, Yingzi.

431
00:20:34,230 --> 00:20:35,290
You're too polite.

432
00:20:35,440 --> 00:20:37,240
I'll call the broker right away.

433
00:20:37,260 --> 00:20:38,670
We have to meet him.

434
00:20:38,990 --> 00:20:39,590
By the way,

435
00:20:39,830 --> 00:20:41,310
can you take a leave?

436
00:20:42,320 --> 00:20:42,670
Yes.

437
00:20:42,980 --> 00:20:44,050
I'll tell him.

438
00:21:12,250 --> 00:21:12,820
Here

439
00:21:14,000 --> 00:21:14,480
Yang...

440
00:21:14,790 --> 00:21:15,990
Are you Mr. Yang?

441
00:21:16,930 --> 00:21:18,000
Are you

442
00:21:18,380 --> 00:21:19,110
Mrs. Luo?

443
00:21:19,120 --> 00:21:20,450
Yes, I am.

444
00:21:20,800 --> 00:21:21,440
Hello.

445
00:21:21,920 --> 00:21:23,840
This is my partner, Qiu.

446
00:21:23,870 --> 00:21:24,360
Hello.

447
00:21:26,920 --> 00:21:27,660
Okay, then.

448
00:21:28,030 --> 00:21:28,660
Let's talk over there.

449
00:21:28,660 --> 00:21:29,190
OK.

450
00:21:32,960 --> 00:21:34,670
This is Xia Shu's classmate

451
00:21:34,670 --> 00:21:35,710
from abroad.

452
00:21:35,730 --> 00:21:37,050
Yes, he is like that.

453
00:21:37,340 --> 00:21:39,740
A law major doesn't be a lawyer but a broker.

454
00:21:40,960 --> 00:21:41,840
He scared me.

455
00:21:41,940 --> 00:21:43,940
Hello, what would you like to drink?

456
00:21:45,030 --> 00:21:46,360
A cup of coffee, please.

457
00:21:46,440 --> 00:21:48,030
What do you want? Order by yourselves.

458
00:21:48,030 --> 00:21:48,520
I...

459
00:21:49,200 --> 00:21:50,400
I want orange juice.

460
00:21:51,710 --> 00:21:52,480
Orange juice.

461
00:21:52,480 --> 00:21:53,770
Mineral water, please.

462
00:21:53,770 --> 00:21:54,900
Okay, wait a moment.

463
00:21:56,720 --> 00:21:57,560
Mr. Yang,

464
00:21:57,810 --> 00:21:59,360
thank you for your trust.

465
00:21:59,970 --> 00:22:01,080
Could you

466
00:22:01,200 --> 00:22:02,680
introduce us

467
00:22:02,710 --> 00:22:04,790
the situation of this case?

468
00:22:04,870 --> 00:22:05,600
Wait.

469
00:22:06,290 --> 00:22:07,560
I have a question.

470
00:22:08,620 --> 00:22:09,410
Have you

471
00:22:09,980 --> 00:22:11,070
had a lawsuit?

472
00:22:14,540 --> 00:22:16,410
Of course.

473
00:22:17,220 --> 00:22:18,700
This year,

474
00:22:18,900 --> 00:22:20,430
I have dealt with six cases.

475
00:22:20,810 --> 00:22:21,890
And they all won.

476
00:22:22,350 --> 00:22:23,780
The same goes for Qiu.

477
00:22:25,290 --> 00:22:26,840
Xia Shu told me

478
00:22:27,410 --> 00:22:29,530
that you two won

479
00:22:30,200 --> 00:22:31,350
Wang Dafu's case.

480
00:22:34,410 --> 00:22:35,920
I'm sorry.

481
00:22:36,480 --> 00:22:37,630
I don't suspect you,

482
00:22:38,630 --> 00:22:39,340
but Mr. Wei

483
00:22:39,750 --> 00:22:42,310
always asked me to find

484
00:22:42,910 --> 00:22:44,310
a sophisticated lawyer.

485
00:22:44,570 --> 00:22:46,830
He thinks a sophisticated lawyer is like

486
00:22:47,070 --> 00:22:48,470
an old doctor.

487
00:22:49,040 --> 00:22:50,500
Experience is important.

488
00:22:50,670 --> 00:22:51,310
Of course,

489
00:22:51,790 --> 00:22:53,620
the case is crucial

490
00:22:53,650 --> 00:22:55,080
to him.

491
00:22:55,120 --> 00:22:56,510
It's a matter of life and death.

492
00:22:56,510 --> 00:22:57,230
So,

493
00:22:57,600 --> 00:22:59,000
he can't take it lightly.

494
00:22:59,990 --> 00:23:00,550
Mr. Yang.

495
00:23:00,570 --> 00:23:01,440
Mr. Yang,

496
00:23:02,020 --> 00:23:03,790
don't worry.

497
00:23:06,760 --> 00:23:08,060
A lawyer

498
00:23:08,300 --> 00:23:10,740
treats all cases equally.

499
00:23:10,940 --> 00:23:12,540
Actually, today, we're here

500
00:23:12,790 --> 00:23:14,030
as vanguards.

501
00:23:14,470 --> 00:23:15,950
We still have our mentor,

502
00:23:16,420 --> 00:23:18,220
who will handle the case with us.

503
00:23:18,240 --> 00:23:18,830
Right?

504
00:23:19,270 --> 00:23:20,310
Our mentor

505
00:23:20,470 --> 00:23:22,510
is a domestic authority,

506
00:23:22,530 --> 00:23:24,220
and has never lost a lawsuit.

507
00:23:26,990 --> 00:23:27,850
How about this?

508
00:23:28,920 --> 00:23:30,840
Ask your mentor out

509
00:23:30,870 --> 00:23:32,470
and have a talk with Mr. Wei.

510
00:23:33,310 --> 00:23:33,870
You see.

511
00:23:34,110 --> 00:23:35,550
I'm just a broker.

512
00:23:35,920 --> 00:23:36,870
Well...

513
00:23:36,900 --> 00:23:38,470
about the final candidate and the way of choosing,

514
00:23:38,470 --> 00:23:38,730
it's

515
00:23:39,180 --> 00:23:40,770
up to Mr. Wei.

516
00:23:41,070 --> 00:23:41,910
Yes.

517
00:23:42,430 --> 00:23:44,150
I understand, Mr. Yang.

518
00:23:44,900 --> 00:23:46,390
How about this, Mr. Yang?

519
00:23:46,420 --> 00:23:48,190
Now that our mentor sented us out,

520
00:23:48,190 --> 00:23:50,190
it's awkward for us to go back empty-handed.

521
00:23:50,190 --> 00:23:51,700
Please introduce this case

522
00:23:51,700 --> 00:23:52,980
to us.

523
00:23:53,470 --> 00:23:56,070
We'll report to our mentor later.

524
00:23:56,870 --> 00:23:57,790
After that,

525
00:23:57,790 --> 00:23:59,850
we won't talk vaguely and generally,

526
00:24:00,190 --> 00:24:01,470
but be more targeted.

527
00:24:01,550 --> 00:24:03,610
Then we can get straight to the point.

528
00:24:04,990 --> 00:24:05,720
OK.

529
00:24:07,030 --> 00:24:09,100
This is all the information about Mr. Wei's case.

530
00:24:09,100 --> 00:24:11,030
Take it back and read it carefully.

531
00:24:11,320 --> 00:24:13,180
This case is significant.

532
00:24:13,620 --> 00:24:15,130
If we fail,

533
00:24:15,870 --> 00:24:18,070
Mr. Wei will lose all the fruits

534
00:24:19,780 --> 00:24:21,110
made in most of his life.

535
00:24:24,260 --> 00:24:25,720
Look forward to seeing your mentor soon.

536
00:24:25,720 --> 00:24:27,280
Okay, let's meet again.

537
00:24:27,470 --> 00:24:27,800
Okay.

538
00:24:28,020 --> 00:24:29,030
Goodbye, Mr. Yang.

539
00:24:29,030 --> 00:24:29,390
Okay.

540
00:24:29,510 --> 00:24:30,100
Bye.

541
00:24:35,930 --> 00:24:38,500
How could you say that? Do we have a mentor?

542
00:24:38,990 --> 00:24:39,950
We'll see.

543
00:24:40,550 --> 00:24:42,010
Let's talk about it later.

544
00:25:00,620 --> 00:25:02,170
It's pretty close.

545
00:25:03,400 --> 00:25:05,470
I want to say something serious.

546
00:25:06,210 --> 00:25:07,070
From tomorrow,

547
00:25:07,240 --> 00:25:07,990
we

548
00:25:08,240 --> 00:25:09,990
should wear shabby clothes,

549
00:25:10,150 --> 00:25:11,810
and show a gloomy expression.

550
00:25:13,150 --> 00:25:14,080
Being envied

551
00:25:14,350 --> 00:25:16,070
may get us killed.

552
00:25:17,040 --> 00:25:18,500
Yingzi, I really envy you.

553
00:25:19,530 --> 00:25:20,690
For what?

554
00:25:22,540 --> 00:25:23,440
You can live

555
00:25:23,480 --> 00:25:24,740
so happily at any time.

556
00:25:26,750 --> 00:25:27,750
You need to live no matter cry

557
00:25:27,750 --> 00:25:28,550
or smile.

558
00:25:28,550 --> 00:25:29,910
Why don't you live with a smile?

559
00:25:29,910 --> 00:25:30,510
Qiu Hua,

560
00:25:30,720 --> 00:25:32,120
you are too serious.

561
00:25:32,520 --> 00:25:32,980
Coming.

562
00:25:38,390 --> 00:25:40,520
Have you decided what to eat for lunch?

563
00:25:41,760 --> 00:25:43,550
Let's eat at the convenience store.

564
00:25:43,550 --> 00:25:44,630
Let me tell you.

565
00:25:44,730 --> 00:25:47,030
A Japanese restaurant just opened. It is 50% off.

566
00:25:47,030 --> 00:25:49,090
I heard that the chef came from Japan.

567
00:25:49,570 --> 00:25:50,680
Sushi, my treat.

568
00:25:51,320 --> 00:25:53,050
I don't want you to spend money.

569
00:25:53,150 --> 00:25:54,280
Where are you going?

570
00:25:54,520 --> 00:25:55,270
Get to work.

571
00:25:56,780 --> 00:25:57,420
Xia Shu.

572
00:26:00,890 --> 00:26:01,960
I told you so many times.

573
00:26:01,960 --> 00:26:04,430
I don't want to go. Why must I go?

574
00:26:06,130 --> 00:26:08,260
What do your parents have to do with me?

575
00:26:09,710 --> 00:26:10,570
I'm hanging up.

576
00:26:13,220 --> 00:26:14,260
What's going on?

577
00:26:15,330 --> 00:26:16,370
Boyfriend?

578
00:26:16,780 --> 00:26:17,980
Isn't he annoying?

579
00:26:18,380 --> 00:26:20,710
He asked me to go home to visit his parents.

580
00:26:20,990 --> 00:26:22,030
His parents' home is in the countryside.

581
00:26:22,030 --> 00:26:23,630
How can I live there?

582
00:26:23,910 --> 00:26:24,470
Besides,

583
00:26:24,710 --> 00:26:25,970
I have nothing to do with his parents.

584
