868
00:38:19,010 --> 00:38:20,780
Sorry, I can't help you.

869
00:38:21,550 --> 00:38:23,210
I have a lot to do in the office.

870
00:38:23,240 --> 00:38:24,020
Go ahead, please.

871
00:38:24,020 --> 00:38:24,620
Come on.

872
00:38:24,640 --> 00:38:25,720
Please.

873
00:38:29,360 --> 00:38:30,200
What the hell!

874
00:38:31,390 --> 00:38:31,990
I knew it.

875
00:38:32,010 --> 00:38:33,190
It's an arduous and thankless task.

876
00:38:33,190 --> 00:38:34,320
No one wants to do it.

877
00:38:34,510 --> 00:38:36,190
I don't believe we can't find help.

878
00:38:36,190 --> 00:38:38,270
You're experienced.

879
00:38:38,600 --> 00:38:40,990
Please help us out.

880
00:38:41,060 --> 00:38:42,070
Now,

881
00:38:42,510 --> 00:38:44,310
I'm not qualified to be a lawyer.

882
00:38:44,790 --> 00:38:46,520
If I present myself as a lawyer,

883
00:38:47,100 --> 00:38:48,640
I am cheating your client.

884
00:38:48,940 --> 00:38:49,690
I'm not going.

885
00:38:49,690 --> 00:38:50,380
Ms. Mei,

886
00:38:50,910 --> 00:38:53,560
without a mentor,

887
00:38:53,830 --> 00:38:55,910
we wouldn't be able to take this case.

888
00:38:58,160 --> 00:38:59,040
Luo Yingzi,

889
00:39:00,110 --> 00:39:01,990
are you confident about this case?

890
00:39:01,990 --> 00:39:02,680
Ms. Mei,

891
00:39:03,090 --> 00:39:05,250
we've made a complete agenda.

892
00:39:05,470 --> 00:39:07,350
This is the only way to win.

893
00:39:07,380 --> 00:39:08,780
We are fully confident.

894
00:39:11,650 --> 00:39:14,200
Then, show your strength

895
00:39:14,550 --> 00:39:16,030
to the client,

896
00:39:16,240 --> 00:39:17,920
move him

897
00:39:17,990 --> 00:39:18,920
and get the case.

898
00:39:19,890 --> 00:39:20,450
But...

899
00:39:22,270 --> 00:39:22,910
Forget it.

900
00:39:24,790 --> 00:39:26,350
Ms. Mei, we're leaving.

901
00:39:27,820 --> 00:39:29,410
Let's find another way.

902
00:39:32,910 --> 00:39:33,470
Yingzi,

903
00:39:34,020 --> 00:39:34,820
wait a minute.

904
00:39:38,740 --> 00:39:39,930
Zhang Shilan

905
00:39:40,870 --> 00:39:42,500
always falls asleep in class.

906
00:39:42,500 --> 00:39:43,490
And now,

907
00:39:44,080 --> 00:39:46,080
she often hangs out with people in society.

908
00:39:46,080 --> 00:39:46,830
Do you know?

909
00:39:46,860 --> 00:39:47,500
No.

910
00:39:47,590 --> 00:39:48,540
Who was she with?

911
00:39:49,760 --> 00:39:52,240
She's often picked up in a limousine.

912
00:39:52,560 --> 00:39:53,470
What's more,

913
00:39:53,690 --> 00:39:55,490
she had a lot of jewellery on her.

914
00:39:56,670 --> 00:39:58,800
You are the one who introduced her here.

915
00:39:58,800 --> 00:40:00,400
I have to tell you about that.

916
00:40:01,400 --> 00:40:03,530
I know. I'll talk to her.

917
00:40:03,990 --> 00:40:04,450
Yingzi.

918
00:40:07,280 --> 00:40:08,540
I'll let you guys talk.

919
00:40:09,590 --> 00:40:10,590
Goodbye, Ms. Mei.

920
00:40:13,250 --> 00:40:14,730
Yingzi, it's you.

921
00:40:14,750 --> 00:40:17,280
I saw your car downstairs when I was going out.

922
00:40:17,510 --> 00:40:19,270
How are you doing here?

923
00:40:19,830 --> 00:40:20,750
Not bad.

924
00:40:22,150 --> 00:40:23,370
Yingzi,

925
00:40:23,580 --> 00:40:26,250
do not talk too much with that old witch. She's mean.

926
00:40:26,250 --> 00:40:28,090
Lanlan, mind your words.

927
00:40:28,300 --> 00:40:30,070
Ms. Mei is a very respected teacher

928
00:40:30,070 --> 00:40:31,750
in the legal profession.

929
00:40:31,910 --> 00:40:33,990
Then why is she teaching here?

930
00:40:34,330 --> 00:40:35,410
You have no idea

931
00:40:35,440 --> 00:40:36,900
that she always scolds me.

932
00:40:37,900 --> 00:40:40,030
You are the one that should be scolded.

933
00:40:40,270 --> 00:40:41,860
You want to study law.

934
00:40:42,000 --> 00:40:43,160
She is your teacher.

935
00:40:47,940 --> 00:40:48,940
Qiu Hua,

936
00:40:48,960 --> 00:40:50,090
I need to talk to her.

937
00:40:54,010 --> 00:40:54,670
Have a seat.

938
00:41:10,170 --> 00:41:10,970
What's wrong?

939
00:41:14,520 --> 00:41:17,050
Have you been in touch with Mr. Zhou recently?

940
00:41:19,440 --> 00:41:20,840
How did you know?

941
00:41:22,030 --> 00:41:23,490
Did he tell you about that?

942
00:41:23,860 --> 00:41:24,370
No.

943
00:41:25,790 --> 00:41:26,800
Why are you

944
00:41:27,120 --> 00:41:28,060
so shy?

945
00:41:31,580 --> 00:41:32,510
We're together.

946
00:41:32,630 --> 00:41:33,470
Together?

947
00:41:36,820 --> 00:41:38,170
What do you mean?

948
00:41:38,540 --> 00:41:39,460
What did you do?

949
00:41:41,410 --> 00:41:42,530
I plan to

950
00:41:43,010 --> 00:41:44,210
give him a baby.

951
00:41:46,510 --> 00:41:47,430
Lanlan,

952
00:41:47,590 --> 00:41:49,520
Mr. Zhou has a family.

953
00:41:49,780 --> 00:41:50,700
I know.

954
00:41:51,290 --> 00:41:53,810
So I have to do it step by step.

955
00:41:56,060 --> 00:41:57,320
Step by step?

956
00:41:57,440 --> 00:41:58,970
What are you talking about?

957
00:42:00,020 --> 00:42:01,530
I'll give him a baby first.

958
00:42:01,830 --> 00:42:04,030
He can't let his child be illegitimate.

959
00:42:04,070 --> 00:42:05,910
Then, I'll ask him to divorce his wife.

960
00:42:05,910 --> 00:42:07,530
Lanlan, you are ruining his family.

961
00:42:07,530 --> 00:42:08,460
Do you know that?

962
00:42:08,870 --> 00:42:10,440
What are you talking about?

963
00:42:10,930 --> 00:42:12,090
We are true love.

964
00:42:12,230 --> 00:42:14,400
What is true love?

965
00:42:14,720 --> 00:42:16,400
Who is Mr. Zhou?

966
00:42:17,040 --> 00:42:18,500
He is a sophisticated man,

967
00:42:19,110 --> 00:42:21,400
who makes Internet loans in Jingbei.

968
00:42:21,710 --> 00:42:23,910
How could he be trapped by a little girl?

969
00:42:24,070 --> 00:42:25,340
Even if you have his baby,

970
00:42:25,340 --> 00:42:27,000
what if he refuses to divorce?

971
00:42:27,430 --> 00:42:29,490
Are you raising the child on your own?

972
00:42:30,230 --> 00:42:31,480
Don't worry, Yingzi.

973
00:42:31,990 --> 00:42:33,790
Since I can give birth to his child,

974
00:42:33,790 --> 00:42:35,750
I can let him divorce his wife for me.

975
00:42:35,750 --> 00:42:37,110
If he refuses to divorce,

976
00:42:37,110 --> 00:42:38,170
I won't let him off.

977
00:42:39,350 --> 00:42:40,810
Lanlan, you are too naive.

978
00:42:42,060 --> 00:42:43,440
You are a moth to a flame, you know?

979
00:42:43,440 --> 00:42:44,570
It's too dangerous.

980
00:42:45,350 --> 00:42:46,000
Sure,

981
00:42:46,190 --> 00:42:47,790
Mr. Zhou is a married man.

982
00:42:47,820 --> 00:42:49,220
He is a scoundrel to do so.

983
00:42:50,120 --> 00:42:52,070
But Lanlan, listen to me,

984
00:42:52,880 --> 00:42:54,050
leave him now.
